Subject: Re: [VB] Anti-Seize and spark plugs

Gene Berg used to not recommend the use of anti-seize on spark plugs.  
He was concerned that the stuff would thermally insulate the plugs  
from the heads. Of course with Gene we all had to do what he  
said.....  Gary
